  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + Rigor Declaration">
      Output: "🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: STANDARD — data seed; no `.cs` modification". Read project CLAUDE.md + spec.md FR-04.
    </step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">
      Verify task 001 ✅. Update `current-task.md` to task 004.
    </step>
    <step order="2" name="Extract Canonical Text">
      Open `SprkChatAgentFactory.cs`; locate `BuildDefaultSystemPrompt()`; capture the EXACT text returned (preserve whitespace + escape sequences). Save to a `notes/task-004-system-prompt-source.txt` for record.
    </step>
    <step order="3" name="Inspect Existing Seed Mechanism">
      Search repo for existing scope seed patterns. Document the chosen mechanism in task notes.
    </step>
    <step order="4" name="Author Seed Script / Data Row">
      Create idempotent seed: row with name "SYS-DEFAULT", description "Default Spaarke AI persona; fallback when no tenant or playbook override exists", scopeType=Global, parentScopeId=null, systemPrompt={verbatim text from Step 2}. Ensure script checks for existing row first (idempotent).
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="🛑 Confirmation Gate — Data Seed Deployment">
      PAUSE per project CLAUDE.md §Confirmation Triggers (data change to production Dataverse entity). Present seed script + verbatim text to user; request approval to deploy.
    </step>
    <step order="6" name="Deploy to Spaarke Dev">
      After confirmation: run seed via `dataverse-deploy` skill / `pac solution import` / Web API call. Verify row exists.
    </step>
    <step order="7" name="Verify Verbatim Match">
      Query the row via Web API + diff against captured text from Step 2 (character-for-character). Any mismatch = HARD FAIL; rerun seed.
    </step>
    <step order="8" name="Verify Idempotency">
      Re-run the seed script. Confirm: existing row not duplicated; no data destruction.
    </step>
    <step order="9" name="Verify Acceptance Criteria">
      Walk each criterion below; record evidence.
    </step>
    <step order="10" name="Document + Complete">
      Update task POML status complete. TASK-INDEX 004 ✅. Reset `current-task.md`. Report. Note BFF publish-size delta = 0 MB.
    </step>
  </steps>

